FilmPress Requests plugin enables film sites to collect geocoded requests to see a given film.

== Description ==

FilmPress Requests plugin enables film sites to collect geocoded requests to see a given film.

== Installation ==

1. Upload `plugin-name.php` to the `/wp-content/plugins/` directory
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress
3. Done!

